{"tid":1254650,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"Metal Build 討論區 （26）：你老母搶唔到，唔該爆post先開新","createTime":"2019-06-24T08:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T08:34:04.000Z","uid":18337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e022c0c6f4886812a8ae5961913d20476af77a27","tid":1254650,"uid":18337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"Metal Build 系列常用資訊網：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sp.tamashii.jp/item_brand/metal_build\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsp.tamashii.jp%2Fitem_brand%2Fmetal_build&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=5188e2bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://sp.tamashii.jp/item_brand/metal_build</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面有哂所有會出同出過既作品同出品年月份<br />\n（除左魂限OO Raiser)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂魂限？<br />\nA:經p-bandai 網上訂購的限定版<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂魂展限？<br />\nA:每年日本秋葉原Tamashii Nation 展覽的會場限定版除左上面提個盒Trans-am OOR，全部都在展後推出相同的魂限<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂普通販賣？<br />\nA:即就咁普通係鋪頭賣買既產品<br />\n<br />\nQ:咩版最好QC?<br />\nA:無論行、日、亞，QC都一樣，同為made in China<br />\n<br />\n常用訂購網：<br />\n<a href=\"http://amiami.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famiami.com&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=7b472577\" target=\"_blank\">http://amiami.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://1999.co.jp/eng/gundam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1999.co.jp%2Feng%2Fgundam&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=810773c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://1999.co.jp/eng/gundam</a><br />\n<br />\n魂限網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"http://p-bandai.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.hk&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=9f8b180e\" target=\"_blank\">http://p-bandai.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://p-bandai.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.jp&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=3f59ebba\" target=\"_blank\">http://p-bandai.jp</a><br />\n<br />\nF91 Q &amp;A<br />\nQ:換頭要連個長方體換 好撚難除<br />\nA:除BACKPACK就得<br />\n<br />\nQ:插落去個架度個兩粒野係邊度<br />\nA:主體盒 右下角 透明袋入面<br />\n<br />\nQ:兩邊肩有虛位<br />\nA:睇說明書，有得拍返埋<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊度買<br />\nA:精品孤仔睡記<br />\n<br />\nQ:買日定行<br />\nA:無分別<br />\n<br />\nQ: OOQ用咩電<br />\nA: LR41*2<br />\n<br />\nQ: exia 點分初版再版<br />\nA:初版左下角logo行字有多一個&lsquo;MBS&rsquo; ,再版係無既<br />\n<br />\nQ: freedom 點分初版再版<br />\nA: 初版紫再版藍（未有實質證據支持）<br />\n<br />\nQ: xxx依家個價抵唔抵<br />\nA: 有愛就買啦屌你<br />\n<br />\nQ: 女神手軟點算<br />\nA: 未過7日就send 返比睡記換<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該爆1001先開新<br />\n請善用會員模式</span></span>"},{"pid":"e5574d5044404582d6a1a50921d065f899f94da2","tid":1254650,"uid":47287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"你老母<br />\n收到SMS 入CODE比錢後再ERROR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9699d3368552d8a87a272405e8c102207459c0","tid":1254650,"uid":33903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"27呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再開過啦"},{"pid":"75d16bdf04bdcca38e19bf91aff25ddb30face2a","tid":1254650,"uid":18337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"又打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（<del>26</del>）"},{"pid":"de8347711866dbbdf892e5e0cd995e8aef21c290","tid":1254650,"uid":18337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b9699d3368552d8a87a272405e8c102207459c0","tid":1254650,"uid":33903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"27呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再開過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"開左"},{"pid":"b8f2003ed090283f91433177063e3e252ddb374d","tid":1254650,"uid":252425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" 